xyz.thepathfinder.android

Class Action

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.thepathfinder.android.Action

  • public class Action
extends Object
    Actions represent transport and commodity actions, such as picking up a commodity, dropping off a commodity, or a transport start location. Actions occur at specific locations and an associated model.
